text: After months of lockdowns, all states have now eased restrictions in some capacity, and many are relying on data to tell them when it is safe to move to the next phase of reopening. But each state has its own idea of what that data should be. https://t.co/IgCkp9NhEn https://t.co/6BkpuoKEc5

text: Starbucks, Chipotle and Shake Shack said they are asking property owners to renegotiate leases or offer deferred rent payments. “We expect that they will partner with us during this difficult time.” https://t.co/jpwVf8N4Vr
